thani oruvan ( english : thani oruvan ) is a 2015 indian tamil action comedy film written and directed by mohan raja . the film features jayam ravi , nayanthara , arvind swamy , nayantara , arvind swamy , nayantara , arvind swamy , nayantara , arvind swamy and nayantara in the lead roles and music composed by yuvan shankar raja . the film was dubbed in telugu as thani oruvan .